  "text": "The physical map presented here is presently being used to facilitate studies on the sequence organization, coding potential and expression of Ki MSV in relation to the phenotype of the infected cell (see [CITATION_1] Avery et'aL, 1980) . We would like to thank the Cancer Research Campaign for generously supporting this work.",
